# Git Conventions

Conventional Commits: `type(scope): description`

Types: `feat`, `fix`, `test`, `refactor`, `chore`, `docs`

```
feat(domain): implement BB-CALC-01 cost calculator
fix(export): align CSV headers and computed cost (D-1)
```

Branches: `feat/*`, `fix/*`, `chore/*` off `develop`.
One concern per PR. Golden fixtures must not be weakened.
